OL,3,CFolk singer hits back after 'lower
OL,4,Cclass northern accent' jibe
OL,6,FA folk singer from Teesside has spoken
OL,7,Fout against accent prejudice after a
OL,8,Fjibe about her "lower class northern
OL,9,Faccent" from an online critic.
OL,11,FAmelia Coburn, from Middlesbrough,
OL,12,Fcondemned a review of her album from a
OL,13,Fmember of public which described her
OL,14,Faccent has not "quite fit(ting) the
OL,15,Fstyle of music".
