OL,3,CFolk singer hits back after 'lower
OL,4,Cclass northern accent' jibe
OL,6,FThe singer and musician told ITV Tyne
OL,7,FTees that while she believed the
OL,8,Fremark stemmed from a place of
OL,9,F"ignorance", she hoped sharing it
OL,10,Fwould make people think again before
OL,11,Fmaking "sweeping generalisations".
OL,13,F"Just stereotyping me as working
OL,14,Fclass, or being stereotyped as being
OL,15,Fthick or unintelligent is just mad
OL,16,Fbecause it's not always true," she
OL,17,Fsaid. "It's weird that this prejudice
OL,18,Fis openly accepted."
