OL,3,CFolk singer hits back after 'lower
OL,4,Cclass northern accent' jibe
OL,6,FAmelia posted on social media about
OL,7,Fthe remark she received, and said she
OL,8,Fwas overwhelmed by the response from
OL,9,Fthose who had experienced similar
OL,10,Fnegative feedback as a result of their
OL,11,Faccents.
OL,13,F"I couldn't believe how many people
OL,14,Fhad gone through the same thing - not
OL,15,Fjust in the North East but all across
OL,16,Fthe country," she said.
OL,18,F"Two hundred people replied on
OL,19,FTwitter. It was quite nice to have
OL,20,Fthat solidarity from other people."
