OL,3,CFolk singer hits back after 'lower
OL,4,Cclass northern accent' jibe
OL,6,FThe singer said it was not the first
OL,7,Ftime her accent had attracted
OL,8,Funwelcome attention which "crossed the
OL,9,Fline".
OL,11,F"I've had teachers say if you're in a
OL,12,Fjob interview for example that I
OL,13,Fshould tone down my accent or the way
OL,14,FI speak so I can be taken seriously,"
OL,15,Fshe explained.
OL,17,F"I've gone to uni and I've had not
OL,18,Fjust had students but lecturers take
OL,19,Fthe mick out of how I speak or how I
OL,20,Fsay things."
