OL,3,CFolk singer hits back after 'lower
OL,4,Cclass northern accent' jibe
OL,6,FFor Amelia, as a folk singer however,
OL,7,Fher identity and northern roots are
OL,8,Fsomething she celebrates in her music.
OL,10,FAmelia Coburn's accent can be detected
OL,11,Fin a song from her new album which was
OL,12,Ffilmed at South Gare in Redcar Credit:
OL,13,FAmelia Coburn, YouTube
OL,15,F"I'm really proud of being from
OL,16,FTeesside. I always have been. I went
OL,17,Fto uni and I came back home because I
OL,18,Flove it. That does run through my
OL,19,Fmusic.
