OL,3,CFolk singer hits back after 'lower
OL,4,Cclass northern accent' jibe
OL,6,F"Growing up in Middlesbrough, near the
OL,7,Fcoast, I've got a lot of maritime
OL,8,Fthemes that pervade my lyrics. I've
OL,9,Falways wanted be a champion of the
OL,10,Farea in my music, and have the accent
OL,11,Fand not change the way I am for other
OL,12,Fpeople."
OL,14,FAlex Cunningham MP, speaking out in
OL,15,Fsupport of Amelia on X, said: "This is
OL,16,Fsimply appalling that anyone can be
OL,17,Fdiscriminated against in this way. I'm
OL,18,Fproud to be a Scot AND an adopted
OL,19,FTeessider thus the at times confusing
OL,20,Faccent."
